17.5 If the contract is concluded with a consumer whose residence is in a member state of the European Union (excluding Austria), Iceland, Norway, or Switzerland, only the court competent for the consumer’s place of residence is responsible.
§ 18 Miscellaneous
18.1 Unless otherwise provided, a deadline begins with the receipt of the corresponding document by the contracting party, who is obliged to observe it. When calculated in days, the day on which the triggering event occurs is not counted; when set in weeks or months, the specified weekday or month applies – if that day does not exist in the month, the last day of the month is decisive.
